snippet.textDisplay:
O the Martyrs of True pathway
Pictures of loyalty faithfulness
wind of our Country Pays you Greetings.
O the Martyrs of True pathway
.
Those who came to burn our homeland,
That Embers (flames) extinguished by your own Blood,
you saved so many flowers (Sons and Daughters) for  becoming Orphans,
you saved so many (spring) Wives for becoming Widowed.
 Winds of garden pay you greetings.
O the Martyrs of True pathway

When had you gone to the battle ground after Drank a glass of  martyrdom ,
Prophet (peace be upon him) Folded You in arms.
Ali (R.A) got happy For you bravery,
Hussein (R.A) Said that,
Hope Of GOD Pays You Greetings,,,
O the Martyrs of True pathway
